00:24:29,062 --> 00:24:31,272
Kami beli pemurni air
Penyair Jeong Geum-seon,

371
00:24:31,356 --> 00:24:33,942
toilet Penyair Yun Seok-yeong,

372
00:24:34,025 --> 00:24:35,735
kami bahkan beli kursi pijat

373
00:24:35,819 --> 00:24:37,362
Penulis Yu Min-su.

374
00:24:37,445 --> 00:24:38,822
Kami sudah punya itu semua.

375
00:24:39,364 --> 00:24:40,198
Selamat siang.

376
00:24:41,533 --> 00:24:43,785
Mari percepat perilisan buku Nona Kang.

377
00:24:43,910 --> 00:24:45,286
Nona Song, lakukan cek ulang.

378
00:24:45,370 --> 00:24:47,580
Pak Bae, cek pengaturan pencetak.

379
00:24:47,747 --> 00:24:48,832
- Baik.
