381
00:24:52,711 --> 00:24:54,462
Kau kenal Penyair Choi Hyeong-su?

382
00:24:54,546 --> 00:24:56,339
Dia menulis puisi tentang musim semi.

383
00:24:56,423 --> 00:24:58,633
