384
00:24:58,842 --> 00:25:00,719
Bernilai sastra, sangat bermakna.

385
00:25:02,512 --> 00:25:04,472
Apa? Apa maksudnya ini?

386
00:25:05,807 --> 00:25:06,683
Hei, Eun-ho.

