hanya terjual 240 eksemplar.

396
00:25:30,915 --> 00:25:32,417
Itu berarti

397
00:25:32,667 --> 00:25:34,502
dia hanya dibayar 240.000 won.

398
00:25:34,586 --> 00:25:37,047
Pikirmu berapa yang didapat
perusahaan penerbit

399
00:25:37,130 --> 00:25:38,882
